    <h3><a href="http://features.pewforum.org/muslim-population-graphic/">The Future of the Global Muslim Population</a></h3>
        <p>These maps allow users to select a country, a region or the world &#8212; as well as decade &#8212; and see the size of the Muslim population in that place and time.</p>
        <p>The feature covers 232 countries and territories over five decades, including population estimates for 1990-2010 and estimates for 2020 and 2030.</p>
        <p class="role"><b>role:</b> user interface design and information architecture</p>
    
